We Are Devs & Logic

A passionate team of developers and designers building innovative SaaS solutions and MVPs for businesses worldwide.

Our Story

Founded in 2015, Devs & Logic was born from a simple vision: to create innovative digital solutions that help businesses thrive in the modern world. What started as a small team of passionate developers has grown into a full-service digital product agency specializing in SaaS applications and MVPs.

Based in the heart of New York City's tech scene, we've collaborated with startups, scaleups, and established enterprises across various industries, from fintech and healthcare to education and e-commerce. Our approach combines technical excellence with strategic thinking to deliver products that not only work flawlessly but also drive business growth.

We believe that great software is built by great teams. That's why we've assembled a diverse group of talented individuals who bring unique perspectives and specialized skills to every project. Our collaborative environment encourages innovation and continuous learning, ensuring we stay at the forefront of emerging technologies and best practices.

Our Process

How we transform your vision into a successful digital product

Step 1

Discovery & Planning

We start by understanding your business objectives, target audience, and specific requirements to create a solid project roadmap.

Step 2

Design & Prototyping

Our designers create intuitive interfaces and user experiences that align with your brand identity and business goals.

Step 3

Development

Our expert developers build your solution using modern technologies and best practices to ensure scalability and performance.

Step 4

Testing & QA

Rigorous testing across devices and platforms ensures your application is bug-free and delivers an exceptional user experience.

Step 5

Deployment

We deploy your application to production with careful attention to performance, security, and reliability.

Step 6

Support & Maintenance

Our relationship doesn't end at launch. We provide ongoing support, updates, and optimizations to keep your application running smoothly.
